front.title: •Rite Of Passage
front.gametext: At the beginning of opponent's move phase, target an opponent's character alone at a mobile site and select an adjacent site. Opponent must choose to move target there for free (target cannot move for remainder of turn), lose target or lose 2 Force.
front.lore: There are many different paths to becoming a Jedi, each with its own risks and consequences. A student must choose wisely.
